					<h1 class="entry-title">How to&#8230; Do things.</h1>
					<p class="headline_meta"><abbr class="published" title="2010-11-01">November 1, 2010</abbr></p>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text entry-content">

<!-- AddThis Button Begin -->
<script type="text/javascript">var addthis_product = 'wpp-261';
var addthis_config = {"data_track_clickback":true,"ui_language":"en"};</script><script type="text/javascript" src="//s7.addthis.com/js/250/addthis_widget.js#pubid=wp-4eba012461af283c"></script><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Buttermilk Substitute by joy the baker, on Flickr" href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2010/11/how-to-do-things/"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3457/3986891565_ba089852c4_z.jpg?zz=1" alt="Buttermilk Substitute" width="640" height="427" /></a></p>
<p>I like to show you how to do things&#8230; like <strong><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2009/10/the-best-buttermilk-substitutions/" target="_blank">how to make buttermilk</a></strong> if you&#8217;re fresh out.</p>
<p>I also like to give you things.</p>
<p>This post will combine these two wonders.</p>
<p>At the top of the page you&#8217;ll notice a new page header called <strong><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/november-giveaway/" target="_blank">November Giveaway</a></strong>.  That&#8217;s the page you should be glued to every single day this month.  That&#8217;s the page that will change every day with all sorts of prizes and such.  Visit.  Often.</p>
<p>Now!  Let me show you how I show you how to make things.</p>
<p>Ps.  I&#8217;m glad you&#8217;re here.</p>
<p><span id="more-3795"></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="How To Make Cake Flour by joy the baker, on Flickr" href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2009/09/how-to-make-cake-flour/"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2629/3937610583_e963ab57f2.jpg" alt="How To Make Cake Flour" width="500" height="334" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Buying <strong><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2009/09/how-to-make-cake-flour/" target="_blank">cake flour</a></strong> just seems so silly.  I think you should totally just make your own.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Cast Iron by joy the baker, on Flickr" href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2008/09/learn-to-love-your-cast-iron-skillet/"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3081/2838297519_a65934136f.jpg" alt="Cast Iron" width="500" height="334" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">I&#8217;m in love with my cast iron skillet.  Food maker meets murder weapon.  Do you have one of these?  <strong><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2008/09/learn-to-love-your-cast-iron-skillet/" target="_blank">Here&#8217;s how to season it!</a></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="How to Make Brown Sugar by joy the baker, on Flickr" href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2010/08/how-to-make-brown-sugar/"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4082/4850485685_9c46abceb1.jpg" alt="How to Make Brown Sugar" width="500" height="333" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2010/08/how-to-make-brown-sugar/" target="_blank">How to make the good stuff</a></strong>:  brown sugar.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="IMG_8861.JPG by joy the baker, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/22540992@N03/4881013470/"><img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4121/4881013470_07c8baba8b.jpg" alt="IMG_8861.JPG" width="500" height="333" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">How to make warm dough with mustard and put it in your face.  <strong><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2010/08/how-to-make-soft-pretzels/" target="_blank">How to make soft pretzels</a></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="How to frost a cake- Step four, add caramel by joy the baker, on Flickr" href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2008/03/how-to-frost-a-cake-in-10-pictures/"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2316/2329798241_8a6bd58600.jpg" alt="How to frost a cake- Step four, add caramel" width="500" height="333" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2008/03/how-to-frost-a-cake-in-10-pictures/" target="_blank"><strong>How to frost a freakin&#8217; cake</strong></a>.  You should add this talent to the list of awesome things that you can do.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Speaking of cake.  I want this <strong><a href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2009/08/honey-whole-wheat-pound-cake/" target="_blank">Honey Whole Wheat Pound Cake</a></strong>, right now.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Honey Whole Wheat Pound Cake by joy the baker, on Flickr" href="http://www.joythebaker.com/blog/2009/08/honey-whole-wheat-pound-cake/"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3494/3857893563_f587ef2c8a.jpg" alt="Honey Whole Wheat Pound Cake" width="500" height="334" /></a></p>
