					<dd class="comment odd alt depth-2">
<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-96716">
<p>I didn&#8217;t see a reply &#8211;</p>
<p>Bread flour has more gluten (the gluey stuff &#8212; good for bread, bad for cake).<br />
Cake flour has less gluten (breads won&#8217;t rise correctly)<br />
All-purpose flour is a compromise between them.</p>
